# CODEOWNERS — every PR requires a review from @LukeHackett.
#
# Combined with branch protection on `main` (Settings → Branches → Require
# review from Code Owners), this enforces owner review on every change.
#
# Dependabot PRs: the auto-merge workflow auto-approves them as the bot before
# calling `gh pr merge --auto`, so they satisfy this rule without blocking.
# Human PRs always need a real review.
#
